to initialise as a truffle project - truffle init

- contract folder already had "migration.sol" file to track migrations of other contract.

-ganache cli - npm i -D ganache-cli or npx ganache


- to migrate on specific network :
npx truffle migrate --network name


- to open console : 
npx truffle console --network name

- create a script folder to interact programatically

-truffle test is command for testing all files in test folder

openzeppelin test framework - "npm install --save-dev @openzeppelin/test-helpers"

-OpenZeppelin Test Helpers for very large number support, to check for an event being emitted and to check that a transaction reverts.

link - "https://docs.openzeppelin.com/learn/writing-automated-tests"


to connect with public test networks we need @truffle/hdwallet-provide :
"npm install --save-dev @truffle/hdwallet-provider"